---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { generateOrganizationSchema } from "../lib/schema";

const schema = generateOrganizationSchema();
---

<Layout
  title="About - White Rabbit WCS"
  description="The story of Phoenix's premier West Coast Swing community. Follow the white rabbit into a world where community comes first."
  type="website"
  schema={schema}
>
  <main class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title gradient-text">Follow the White Rabbit</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          The Story of Phoenix's Premier WCS Community
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="story-content">
        <section class="story-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">> The Beginning üêá</h2>
          <p>
            In 2018-2019, Phoenix's West Coast Swing scene had stalled. Younger
            dancers craved modern music and fresh energy, but established venues
            weren't listening. When COVID restrictions lifted in Arizona, we saw
            an opportunity.
          </p>
          <p>
            What started as intimate speakeasy-style home socials, just friends
            dancing in living rooms, evolved into something extraordinary.
            During our final home event, a joke about "90's rave style"
            marketing with bunny stencils and a "Follow the White Rabbit"
            message sparked something real. The name stuck, and White Rabbit
            Society was born.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">> Community First, Always üíö</h2>
          <p>
            White Rabbit isn't about profit. It's about people. We operate on a
            simple philosophy: put the community's needs first, and everything
            else follows.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every year, we survey our dancers. Real voices. Real input. Real
            change. This isn't just our community. It's yours. From 24 dancers
            in a tiny venue to 200 at our monthly socials, we've grown because
            we listen.
          </p>
          <p>
            We celebrate what matters: connection, growth, and the joy of dance.
            Our annual Social Dance Champions aren't crowned by judges. They're
            chosen by you, the community, through democratic voting.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">> What Makes Us Different</h2>
          <p>
            We believe in going far, together. Not fast, alone. This philosophy
            shapes everything we do:
          </p>
          <ul class="features-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Modern Energy:</strong> Contemporary music, fresh vibes, and
              an atmosphere that welcomes everyone
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>True Community:</strong> Annual surveys, democratic voting,
              and genuine care for every dancer's experience
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>All Levels Welcome:</strong> Whether you're stepping onto the
              floor for the first time or you're a seasoned pro, there's a place for
              you here
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Phoenix Proud:</strong> We're building something special right
              here in the Sonoran Desert, and we want you to be part of it
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">> The Journey Continues</h2>
          <p>
            From speakeasy socials to Arizona's biggest monthly West Coast Swing
            event, White Rabbit has become more than a dance community, it's a
            movement. A place where the music is modern, the energy is electric,
            and every dancer matters.
          </p>
          <p>
            The white rabbit led us down this path. Now we're inviting you to
            follow it too.
          </p>
          <p class="cta-text">Ready to see how deep the rabbit hole goes?</p>
        </section>

        <div class="quote-block">
          <blockquote>
            "If you want to go fast, go alone.<br />
            If you want to go far, go together."
          </blockquote>
          <cite>‚Äî African Proverb</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .story-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .features-list li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features-list li::before {
    content: "‚ñ∏";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .features-list strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .quote-block {
    margin: 4rem 0;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  cite {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .story-section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .story-section p,
    .features-list li {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .quote-block {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
